R. G. Springsteen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/R._G._Springsteen 0 Robert G. Springsteen (September 8, 1904 – December 9, 1989) was an American director of Hollywood B movies and television shows. He was most often credited on screen as R. G. Springsteen. Robert_G._Springsteen ( September_8_,_1904 – December_9_,_1989 ) was an_American_director of Hollywood_B_movies_and_television_shows .
